snippet.title: Myles Wright, Ace Attorney - Turnabout Revival
snippet.description:
https://archive.org/details/myles-wright-ace-attorney
The demo of an unreleased fangame by "Thunder84".
Pretty good first case. Set 23 years after Spirit of Justice.
You're the son of Phoenix and Maya. The Judge is still there.
The jury returns.
There were going to be Layton-style "mysteries".
